  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Diagnostic of diabetes in childhood brought modification of family way of life, particularly
      in child and caregivers lifes.

      The education patient programs are in France centered on curative competencies of care.

      It is possible that art-therapy improve psycho-social competencies The aim of the study is to
      evaluate art-therapy sessions on quality of life of caregivers
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
